Package solver.constraints.nary.alldifferent

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllDifferent
    Ensures that all variables from VARS take a different value.
    PropAllDiffAC
    Propagator for AllDifferent AC constraint for integer variables

    Uses Regin algorithm Runs in O(m.n) worst case time for the initial propagation but has a good average behavior in practice

    Runs incrementally for maintaining a matching

    PropAllDiffAdaptative
    Propagator for AllDifferent AC constraint for integer variables

    Uses Regin algorithm Runs in O(m.n) worst case time for the initial propagation but has a good average behavior in practice

    Runs incrementally for maintaining a matching

    PropAllDiffBC
    Based on:
    "A Fast and Simple Algorithm for Bounds Consistency of the AllDifferent Constraint"
    A.
    PropAllDiffInst
    Propagator for AllDifferent that only reacts on instantiation
